  <!-- INTRO -->
    <div class="section">
      <p>Hi,</p>
      <p>Thanks for taking the time to test me out. How did I do? <br>
As promised, here’s a summary of our conversation:</p>

    </div>

<table style="width:100%; max-width:640px; border-collapse:collapse; table-layout:fixed; font-family:'Times New Roman', Times, serif; font-size:11pt; margin:0 auto;">
